insights.title: Champion Personality
insights.summary: You're a top lane brawler who loves champions with massive presence and zone control. Your Urgot and Illaoi picks suggest you enjoy turning teamfights into nightmares for opponents with your chunky, disruptive playstyle.
insights.strength: Incredible teamfight impact with high damage output - averaging 8.8 assists shows you're consistently contributing to your team's success and creating opportunities
insights.weakness: Zero first bloods indicates a passive early game. Focus on trading more aggressively in lane, using champion matchup knowledge to secure early advantages and translate that into map pressure
insights.funFact: With a 40% win rate, you're basically the definition of 'coin flip top laner' - one game you're a monster, next game you're feeding. Time to tip those odds in your favor!
insights.coachTip: Your champion pool shows you love champions that can control space. Lean into that strength, but work on early game tempo to become a true top lane terror!
